lated from the observed data. ML has become one of the hottest fields of study today, taken up by undergraduate and graduate students from 15 different majors at Caltech. This course balances theory and practice, and covers the mathematical as well as the heuristic aspects.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://work.caltech.edu/lectures.html\">Lectures</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://work.caltech.edu/homeworks.html\">Homework</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://work.caltech.edu/textbook.html\">Textbook</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>","updatedAt":"2016-02-24T06:56:21.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"sorrycc/awesome-javascript","categoryHTML":"<h2>ES6</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/rse/es6-features\">es6-features</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/rse/es6-features\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">6.1k</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":6122,\"repo\":\"rse/es6-features\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - ECMAScript 6: Feature Overview &#x26; Comparison.</li>","updatedAt":"2016-02-24T06:43:14.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"sorrycc/awesome-javascript","categoryHTML":"<h2>ES6</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/DrkSephy/es6-cheatsheet\">es6-cheatsheet</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/DrkSephy/es6-cheatsheet\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span s